    <patterns>
      <pattern name="JPS Action authoring with scheduled trigger" location=".claude/skills/jps-action-create/SKILL.md">Same Template format as task 053; add the `trigger` block with `type: "scheduled"` and a cron template string.</pattern>
      <pattern name="Job Contract idempotency" location=".claude/patterns/api/background-workers.md">`IIdempotencyService` deduplicates at-least-once message deliveries. Provide a stable `IdempotencyKey`.</pattern>
